20Anthropic%20technical%20staff%20member%20Stephen%20Grider.%20%26quot%3BReal-World%20AI%20for%20Everyone%26quot%3B%20is%20taught%20by%20AWIT%20founder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faws-nancy-wang-advice-for-job-seekers-in-hiring-freeze-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENancy%20Wang%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20former%20Anthropic%20engineering%20manager%20Dan%20Mellott.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHart%20says%20that%20Anthropic%20was%20methodical.%20Two%20months%20passed%20between%20the%20partnership%20announcement%20and%20the%20debut%20of%20the%20two%20courses%2C%20though%20Hart%20said%20that%20time%20wasn't%20solely%20spent%20on%20course%20creation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20focused%20on%20making%20sure%20that%20they%20had%20the%20right%20material%2C%20because%20they%20have%20such%20a%20focus%20on%20safe%20and%20effective%20use%20of%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20has%20long%20been%20a%20partner%20of%20interest%20for%20Coursera%2C%20Hart%20said%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20before%20he%20joined%20the%20company.%20Hart%20started%20as%20CEO%20in%20February%202025%2C%20having%20spent%20over%2020%20years%20working%20at%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223380%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20one%20new%20Anthropic%20course%20on%20Coursera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691b9bd389026fbb4d0dd20e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221874%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20%26quot%3BReal-World%20AI%20for%20Everyone%26quot%3B%20course%20features%20talks%20from%20Anthropic%20employees.%3Cp%3ECoursera%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20having%20coded%20much%20beyond%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-limits-use-cases-software-companies-airtable-redis-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evibe-coding%20trials%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20decided%20the%20generalist%20course%20was%20right%20for%20me.%20There%20are%20three%20courses%20in%20the%20series%20%E2%80%94%20making%20it%20%26quot%3Blighter%20weight%2C%26quot%3B%20Hart%20said%20%E2%80%94%20and%20each%20section%20has%203-4%20modules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20opening%20advice%20is%20quite%20basic.%20Mellott%20demonstrated%20how%20to%20make%20Claude%20generate%20a%20recipe%20or%20edit%20an%20email.%20Gradually%2C%20the%20advice%20got%20more%20helpful%2C%20even%20showing%20how%20to%20simulate%20a%20job%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20some%20friendly%20faces%20from%20Anthropic%20to%20offer%20advice%20along%20the%20way%2C%20from%20a%20product%20manager%20to%20the%20company's%20head%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20many%20people%20are%20still%20learning%20how%20to%20collaborate%20with%20AI%20safely%20and%20effectively%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthropic's%20head%20of%20education%2C%20Maggie%20Vo%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThese%20courses%20address%20that%20gap%20by%20giving%20learners%20the%20skills%20and%20confidence%20to%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20Claude%2C%20from%20the%20fundamentals%20of%20getting%20started%20up%20to%20building%20agents.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22426f18f0-f82d-454a-9fe6-9a3fd1d71fcf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EInside%20Coursera's%20AI%20boom%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20want%20to%20learn%20about%20AI.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%2C%20in%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFourteen%20new%20people%20enroll%20in%20an%20AI-themed%20course%20per%20minute%2C%20Hart%20said.%20That's%20up%20from%208%20enrollments%20per%20minute%20in%202024%2C%20and%201%20enrollment%20per%20minute%20in%202023.%20Coursera%20now%20has%20over%201%2C100%20AI-themed%20courses%2C%20a%20figure%20that%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20year-over-year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20is%20far%20from%20its%20first%20AI%20partnership.%20Coursera%20has%20built%20courses%20around%20Google%20Gemini%2C%20including%20for%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3