ing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMcCrann%20said%20the%20number%20of%20targets%20drones%20can%20threaten%20has%20expanded%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Ukraine%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-did-russia-invade-ukraine-putin-politics-motive-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERussia's%20drone%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20hit%20not%20just%20military%20infrastructure%20but%20also%20civilian%20and%20energy%20sites%2C%20highlighting%20the%20reach%20and%20effect%20of%20drones%20in%20modern%20warfare.%20Russian%20and%20unidentified%20drones%20have%20also%20appeared%20across%20Europe%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrones-disrupting-denmark-airports-near-f-35-stealth-fighter-base-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edisrupting%20airports%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-f-35-new-kill-mark-after-russian-drone-takedown-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprompting%20Western%20air%20forces%20to%20scramble%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20military%20bases%20and%20even%20some%20major%20sporting%20events%20have%20experienced%20drone-related%20disruptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20in%20camouflage%20gear%20holds%20a%20large%20grey%20drone%20above%20him%20while%20surrounded%20by%20trees%20as%20two%20other%20figures%20stand%20beside%20him%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691b499589026fbb4d0dc4e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkraine%20and%20Russia%20are%20both%20rapidly%20innovating%20new%20types%20of%20drones%2C%20and%20new%20ways%20to%20stop%20them.%3Cp%3EYevhen%20Titov%2FGlobal%20Images%20Ukraine%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20West%2C%20McCrann%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20definitely%20have%20to%20expand%20our%20thinking%20as%20far%20as%20the%20potential%20threats%20and%20how%20