d%20overnight%20before%20a%20rescue%20jet%20arrived%20from%20Copenhagen%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGoose%20Bay%2C%20home%20to%208%2C000%20people%20and%20an%20air%20force%20base%2C%20often%20handles%20emergency%20landings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflying-business-class-sas-scandinavian-airlines-review-photos-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESAS%20Scandinavian%20Airlines%3C%2Fa%3E%20flight%20from%20New%20York%20to%20Copenhagen%20was%20forced%20to%20divert%20to%20a%20Canadian%20military%20base%2C%20leaving%20passengers%20stranded%20overnight%20before%20the%20airline%20dispatched%20a%20rescue%20jet%20to%20retrieve%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlight%20SK910%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbus-rare-jetliner-a330neo-flying-more-places-airlines-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAirbus%20A330%3C%2Fa%3E-300%2C%20departed%20Newark%20Liberty%20International%20Airport%20at%205%3A47%20p.m.%20Eastern%20time%20on%20Sunday%2C%20bound%20for%20Denmark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20three%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20in%20the%20air%2C%20the%20plane%20diverted%20northwest%20and%20landed%20safely%20at%20Goose%20Bay%20Airport%20in%20Labrador%2C%20Canada%2C%20at%209%3A15%20p.m.%20local%20time%20(AST)%2C%20according%20to%20FlightAware%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unclear%20what%20led%20to%20the%20unscheduled%20landing.%20SAS%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20of%20the%20last%20airports%20before%20crossing%20the%20Atlantic%2C%20Goose%20Bay%20is%20frequently%20used%20as%20a%20diversion%20site%20for%20transatlantic%20flights%2C%20but%20offers%20limited%20passenger%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20SAS%20sent%20an%20unloaded%20Airbus%20A330%2C%20operating%20as%20flight%20SK9201%2C%20from%20Copenhagen%20to%20Goose%20Bay%2C%20seemingly%20to%20rescue%20the%20stranded%20passengers.%20It%20took%20off%20from%20Copenhagen%20at%2010%3A55%20a.m.%20local%20time%20on%20Monday%2C%20landing%20just%20after%20midday%20in%20Goose%20Bay%2C%20per%20Flightradar24%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20presumably%20very%20light%20SAS%20A330%20has%20been%20scrambled%20to%20fly%20to%20Goose%20Bay%20to%20pick%20up%20stranded%20passengers%2C%26quot%3B%20Flightradar24%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plane%20took%20off%20again%20for%20Copenhagen%20at%207%3A15%20p.m.%20local%20time%2C%20landing%20in%20the%20Danish%20capital%20around%205%3A30%20a.m.%20on%20Tuesday%20morning.%20As%20such%2C%20passengers%20from%20flight%20SK910%20were%20stranded%20in%20Goose%20Bay%20for%20around%2022%20hours%2C%20also%20arriving%2022%20hours%20late%20at%20their%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unclear%20whether%20the%20passengers%20were%20accommodated%20inside%20the%20military%20base%20%E2%80%94%20though%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-air-lines-passengers-stranded-remote-canadian-town-technical-problems-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esimilar%202023%20incident%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20270%20Delta%20passengers%20stranded%20in%20Goose%20Bay%20were%20housed%20overnight%20in%20military%20barracks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoose%20Bay's%20population%20is%20roughly%208%2C000%2C%20and%20its%20limited%20civilian%20infrastructure%20often%20leaves%20diverted%20passengers%20waiting%20for%20replacement%20aircraft%20or%20crew%20to%20arrive%20from%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20plane%20was%20still%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20Goose%20Bay%20as%20of%205%20a.m.%20ET%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewark-passengers-stranded-overnight-at-canadian-military-base-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763461367000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691b3be1abd5e944effad8c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewark-passengers-stranded-overnight-at-canadian-military-base-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20SAS%20flight%20from%20New%20York%20to%20Copenhagen%20diverted%20to%20a%20remote%20Canadian%20military%20base%2C%20stranding%20passengers%20overnight%20in%20Goose%20Bay.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tspirlet%40insider.com%20(Thibault%20Spirlet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewark-passengers-stranded-overnight-at-canadian-military-base-2025-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20AI%20bubble%20you%20haven't%20heard%20about%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20data%20center%20under%20construction.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690cd25621c3f142ebfc375b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222669%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKyle%20Grillot%2FBloomberg%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20an%20artificial%20intelligence%20bubble%20you%20may%20not%20know%20about%2C%20and%20it%20could%20soon%20come%20for%20your%20electric%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20companies%20that%20provide%20the%20power%20to%20data%20centers%20are%20pushing%20regulators%20to%20approve%20massive%20spending%20increases%20for%20power%20plants%20and%20grid%20infrastructure.%20The%20electricity%20forecasts%20they're%20using%20to%20make%20their%20case%20have%20an%20inflation%20problem%20%E2%80%94%20and%20consumers%20could%20end%20up%20paying%20for%20power%20plants%20they%20may%20never%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20utilities%20are%20citing%20sky-high%20estimates%20to%20justify%20new%20AI%20data%20centers%20from%20Georgia%20to%20Texas%20and%20up%20to%20Minnesota.%20The%20catch%3F%20Data%20center%20operators%20submit%20electricity%20requests%20in%20multiple%20jurisdictions%2C%20hoping%20that%20one%20might%20pan%20out.%20Constellation%20Energy%20CEO%20Joseph%20Dominguez%20compared%20it%20to%20fishing%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20put%20a%20bunch%20of%20lines%20in%20the%20water%20to%20try%20to%20catch%20fish%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20data%20center%20developers%20are%20doing%20exactly%20the%20same%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThink%20of%20it%20this%20way%3A%20A%20developer%20with%20plans%20for%20one%20new%20data%20center%20might%20go%20to%20five%20different%20utilities%2C%20each%20blind%20to%20the%20other%20requests.%20If%20the%20utility%20doesn't%20have%20enough%20capacity%2C%20it%20has%20to%20build%20another%20plant.%20Five%20power%20plants%20might%20get%20built%2C%20paid%20for%20with%20increases%20to%20current%20residential%20and%20commercial%20bills.%20By%20the%20time%20the%20developer%20finalizes%20its%20location%2C%20it%20has%20likely%20abandoned%20the%20other%20four%2C%20leaving%20new%20plants%20in%20places%20without%20increased%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20regulators%20and%20utilities%20are%20cracking%20down%2C%20it%20remains%20a%20widespread%20practice%20%E2%80%94%20and%20concerns%20are%20now%20growing%20amid%20already%20rising%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fenergy-conservation-hacks-data-center-costs-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectricity%20bills%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-business%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInside%20Business%3C%2Fa%3E%20stories%20reveal%20the%20inner%20workings%20of%20companies%20from%20Silicon%20Valley%20to%20Wall%20Street%20that%20are%20shaping%20our%20world%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stakes%20are%20high.%20If%20utilities%20build%20too%20little%2C%20the%20reliability%20of%20the%20grid%20could%20be%20at%20risk.%20If%20utilities%20build%20too%20much%2C%20consumers%20could%20be%20saddled%20for%20decades%20with%20costs%20from%20idle%20power%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUtilities%20are%20%26quot%3Binvesting%20in%20the%20grid%20and%20recovering%20those%20costs%20through%20rates%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mark%20Dyson%2C%20a%20managing%20director%20with%20the%20Rocky%20Mountain%20Institute%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20focused%20on%20promoting%20market-based%20and%20sustainable%20energy%20solutions.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20a%20structural%20incentive%20to%20forecast%20demand%20growth%20in%20excess%20of%20what%20it%20is%20in%20order%20to%20recoup%20more%20returns.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFew%20people%20expect%20the%20utilities%20to%20build%20enough%20generation%20for%20all%20the%20power%20demand%20they're%20forecasting%2C%20said%20Jeremy%20Fisher%2C%20a%20principal%20advisor%20to%20the%20Sierra%20Club%20with%20a%20decade%20of%20experience%20helping%20states%20and%20municipalities%20in%20energy%20resource%20planning.%20But%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20they%20are%20using%20these%20estimates%20to%20lobby%20state%20regulators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20real%20risk%20that%20we're%20already%20paying%20for%20some%20of%20that%20speculative%20load%2C%20or%20will%20be%20paying%20for%20that%20shortly%2C%26quot%3B%20Fisher%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2223aba3fb-409f-4579-bc30-4da4e472a87e%5C%22%3E'That%20creates%20a%20tense%20situation%20for%20everybody'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMcKinsey%20estimates%20that%20data%20centers%20globally%20will%20require%20219%20gigawatts%20of%20electricity%20by%202030.%20Twenty-six%20of%20the%20country's%20largest%20investor-owned%20utilities%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20say%20they%20have%20data%20center%20projects%20that%20will%20require%20711%20gigawatts%20of%20electricity%2C%20according%20to%20estimates%20compiled%20by%20the%20Sierra%20Club%20%E2%80%94%20almost%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20power%20demanded%20by%20the%20continental%20US%20at%20its%20summer%20peak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%20are%20utilities%20forecasting%20such%20lofty%20demand%3F%20The%20answer%20lies%20in%20the%20complex%20interplay%20of%20an%20energy%20system%20incentivized%20to%20build%20more%20power%20plants%20and%20the%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20at%20stake%20in%20the%20artificial%20intelligence%20boom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMajor%20players%20like%20Amazon%2C%20Google%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Meta%20aren't%20directly%20building%20most%20data%20centers.%20Instead%2C%20construction%20lies%20with%20a%20series%20of%20middlemen%20that%20hope%20to%20flip%20the%20properties%20to%20one%20of%20the%20large%20tech%20companies%20or%20their%20smaller%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEveryone%20from%20mom-and-pop%20operators%20to%20established%20real%20estate%20development%20companies%20is%20scrambling%20to%20capture%20a%20slice%20of%20the%20rewards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20player%20takes%20its%20project%20to%20the%20utility%20and%20asks%20for%20electricity.%20Many%20are%20doing%20it%20in%20multiple%20jurisdictions%20in%20the%20hopes%20that%20one%20of%20their%20projects%20will%20be%20able%20to%20secure%20the%20necessary%20power%2C%20according%20to%20experts%20and%20industry%20sources.%20Utilities%20then%20take%20these%20requests%20and%20conduct%20feasibility%20studies%20if%20they%20find%20them%20credible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20from%20conversations%20with%20our%20customers%20and%20end%20users%20that%20the%20same%20data%20center%20need%20is%20being%20considered%20in%20multiple%20jurisdictions%20across%20the%20United%20States%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Constellation%20Energy's%20Dominguez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20those%20requests%20don't%20end%20up%20going%20anywhere%2C%20said%20Astrid%20Atkinson%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20grid%20efficiency%20software%20provider%20Camus%20Energy%20and%20a%20former%20Google%20data%20center%20engineer.%20%26quot%3BAny%20developer%20is%20going%20to%20want%20to%20have%20a%20few%20options%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20as%20those%20sites%20get%20further%20through%20their%20life%20cycle%2C%20some%20of%20them%20are%20going%20to%20make%20it%20and%20some%20of%20them%20are%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAtkinson%2C%20who%20frequently%20speaks%20to%20data%20center%20developers%20and%20builders%2C%20estimated%20that%20there%20may%20be%20between%20five%20and%2010%20times%20the%20demand%20to%20connect%20to%20the%20grid%20as%20there%20will%20be%20data%20centers%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20developers%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20issue.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20just%20going%20around%20dropping%20load%20requests%20in%20the%2019%20markets%20because%20that's%20not%20prudent%3B%20people%20wouldn't%20return%20our%20phone%20calls%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ryan%20Mallory%2C%20the%20CEO%20at%20Flexential%2C%20a%20data%20center%20operator%20with%2042%20facilities%20that's%20backed%20by%20Morgan%20Stanley.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20companies%20that%20do%20that%20%E2%80%94%20some%20newer%20developers%20are%20out%20there%20carpet%20bombing%20markets%2C%20and%20that%20creates%20a%20tense%20situation%20for%20everybody.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20push%20for%20power%20to%20meet%20data%20center%20demand%20is%20further%20complicated%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20aren't%20enough%20semiconductor%20chips%20to%20use%20the%20power.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAMD%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20graphics%20processing%20units%20are%20the%20backbone%20of%20AI%20computing%2C%20and%20typically%20account%20for%20more%20than%20half%20of%20a%20data%20center's%20energy%20use%20%E2%80%94%20will%20produce%20enough%20GPUs%20for%205%20gigawatts%20of%20computing%20power%20this%20year%2C%20growing%20to%209.5%20gigawatts%20by%202028%2C%20according%20to%20Enverus%2C%20an%20energy%20market%20data%20analysis%20and%20consulting%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20assuming%20that%20data%20centers%20require%20twice%20that%20amount%20of%20electricity%20to%20cool%20servers%2C%20keep%20the%20lights%20on%2C%20and%20perform%20other%20tasks%2C%20that's%20only%20around%2019%20gigawatts%20of%20power%20demand.%20There%20aren't%20close%20to%20enough%20GPU%20chips%20in%20the%20world%20to%20use%20the%20power%20utilities%20say%20they%20need%20to%20provide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20market's%20pretty%20smart%2C%20at%20least%20for%20the%20next%20year%20or%20two%2C%20about%20what%20actual%20GPU%20production%20is%20going%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Carson%20Kearl%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Enverus%2C%20which%20based%20its%20estimates%20on%20Wall%20Street's%20revenue%20forecasts%20and%20the%20assumed%20revenue%20from%20each%20chip.%20%26quot%3BThat%20sort%20of%20quantity%20is%20extremely%20detached%20from%20what%20the%20queues%20are%20suggesting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e66ccc09-5700-47b0-b71c-e308da0bc13c%5C%22%3E'Everybody%20competing%20for%20a%20growing%20slice%20of%20the%20pie'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EData%20centers%20represent%20a%20new%20growth%20opportunity%20for%20utilities%2C%20which%20have%20faced%20flat%20or%20declining%20electricity%20demand%20for%20decades%20due%20to%20efficiency%20gains%20in%20things%20like%20lighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20at%20the%20Lawrence%20Berkeley%20National%20Lab%20recently%20found%20that%20data%20centers%20accounted%20for%204.4%25%20of%20total%20US%20electricity%20in%202023%2C%20a%20share%20that%20may%20climb%20to%20between%206.7%25%20to%2012%25%20by%202030.%20Other%20industries%2C%20such%20as%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20have%20also%20contributed%20to%20growing%20electricity%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%202024%2C%20there%20were%201%2C240%20data%20centers%20planned%20or%20operating%20in%20the%20US%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-calculate-data-center-cost-environmental-impact-methodology-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Business%20Insider%20investigation%20published%20earlier%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20every%20permitted%20facility%20came%20online%2C%20their%20electricity%20demand%20could%20reach%20between%20149.6%20terawatt-hours%20and%20239.3%20terawatt-hours%20annually%2C%20Business%20Insider%20found.%20The%20low%20end%20of%20the%20estimate%20is%20roughly%20equivalent%20to%20the%20state%20of%20Ohio's%20electricity%20needs%20in%202023%2C%20and%2C%20on%20the%20high%20end%2C%20nearly%20as%20much%20power%20as%20the%20entire%20state%20of%20Florida%20the%20same%20year.%20A%202024%20federal%20report%20projected%20demand%20could%20reach%20levels%20at%20the%20higher%20end%20of%20Business%20Insider's%20estimates%20by%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20power%20plants%20generating%20more%20electricity%20are%20likely%20necessary%20to%20power%20the%20AI%20boom%2C%20experts%20at%20McKinsey%20and%20Deloitte%20say.%20The%20question%20is%20how%20much%20power%20is%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrid%20Strategies%20releases%20an%20annual%20report%20looking%20at%20just%20that%20question.%20In%20December%202024%2C%20the%20firm%20said%20two%20regions%20led%20the%20pack%20that%20year%20in%20the%20size%20of%20the%20updates%20they%20made%20to%20their%20five-year%20forecasts%20for%20electricity%20demand.%20The%20Electric%20Reliability%20Council%20of%20Texas%2C%20known%20as%20ERCOT%2C%20added%20nearly%2037%20gigawatts%20to%20its%20forecast%3B%20the%20PJM%20Interconnection%2C%20which%20covers%20parts%20of%2013%20states%2C%20including%20the%20data%20center%20capital%20of%20the%20world%20in%20Virginia%2C%20added%20more%20than%2015%20gigawatts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20forecasts%20aggregate%20estimates%20from%20utilities%2C%20which%20have%20historically%20been%20biased%20toward%20forecasting%20more%20load%20growth%20than%20what's%20actually%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20the%20Rocky%20Mountain%20Institute%20published%20a%20report%20noting%20that%20between%202012%20and%202023%2C%20on%20average%2C%20utilities%20overestimated%20demand%20by%2023%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20utility%20brings%20an%20individualized%20approach%20to%20estimating%20load%20growth.%20Louisville%20Gas%20and%20Electric%20and%20Kentucky%20Utilities%20based%20a%20request%20to%20spend%20%243%20billion%20on%20two%20new%20gas%20plants%20on%206%20gigawatts%20of%20demand%20from%20data%20center%20projects%20it%20has%20in%20the%20queue%2C%20according%20to%20documents%20submitted%20to%20state%20regulators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20one%20of%20the%2018%20data%20center%20projects%20in%20its%20service%20area%20was%20found%20to%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20probability%26quot%3B%20of%20locating%20there%2C%20according%20to%20the%20companies'%20March%20response%20to%20regulators%2C%20and%20none%20of%20the%20projects%20had%20signed%20a%20contract.%20Nonetheless%2C%20the%20utility%20said%20it%20thought%20that%201.75%20gigawatts%2C%20or%20nearly%2030%25%20of%20the%20total%2C%20would%20get%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20state%20officials%20signed%20off%20on%20the%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrew%20Gardner%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Kentucky%20utilities%2C%20which%20operate%20jointly%2C%20said%20%26quot%3Bwe%20disagree%20with%20this%20characterization%20of%20our%20generation%20investment%20plans%20and%20how%20we%20operate%20as%20regulated%20utilities%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20the%20two%20new%20plants%20will%20%26quot%3Bsupport%20our%20ability%20to%20continue%20serving%20customers%20safely%20and%20reliably%2C%20while%20keeping%20pace%20with%20Kentucky's%20record-breaking%20economic%20development%20needs.%26quot%3B%20The%20forecast%20for%20record-breaking%20growth%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20dependent%20on%20any%20one%20customer%20or%20project.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%2C%20like%20Dominion%20Energy%2C%20which%20serves%20Virginia's%20%26quot%3BData%20Center%20Alley%2C%26quot%3B%20discount%20more%20speculative%20requests.%20In%20a%20hearing%20in%20front%20of%20the%20North%20Carolina%20Utilities%20Commission%20last%20month%2C%20Dominion%20officials%20said%20the%20company%20had%20about%2054%20data%20center%20customers%2C%20and%20another%2050%20or%20so%20speculative%20customers%2C%20real%20estate%20developers%20or%20other%20individuals%2C%20with%20little%20substantive%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20convinced%20that%20that's%20going%20to%20increase%20actual%20data%20center%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Dominion%20representative%20said%20in%20the%20hearing.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20competition%2C%20everybody%20competing%20for%20a%20growing%20slice%20of%20the%20pie.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAaron%20Ruby%2C%20a%20Dominion%20spokesperson%2C%20said%20that%20at%20Dominion%2C%20demand%20has%20exceeded%20the%20forecast%20%26quot%3Bfor%20several%20years.%26quot%3B%20He%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20whether%20that%20was%20because%20of%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20Dominion%20bases%20its%20%26quot%3Blong-term%20power%20generation%20planning%20on%20PJM's%20load%20forecast%2C%20not%20our%20own.%20We%20independently%20validate%20the%20forecast%20by%20comparing%20it%20to%20the%20load%20we%20have%20under%20contract%20with%20our%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20consistently%20match%20up%2C%20which%20gives%20confidence%20in%20their%20accuracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Wilson%2C%20the%20Grid%20Strategies%20vice%20president%20who%20prepared%20the%20report%20on%20load%20growth%2C%20acknowledged%20that%20utilities%20have%20an%20upward%20bias%2C%20but%20ascribed%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20inflated%20estimates%20to%20a%20need%20for%20new%20load-demand%20forecasting%20methods.%20Until%20about%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20said%2C%20utilities%20used%20population%20and%20economic%20growth%20to%20forecast%20future%20load.%20Now%2C%2080%25%20or%20more%20of%20their%20forecasts%20are%20for%20large%20loads%20like%20data%20centers%20%E2%80%94%20electricity%20demands%20so%20new%2C%20large%2C%20and%20uncertain%20that%20the%20previous%20methods%20aren't%20adequate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20room%20for%20improvement%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Wilson.%20Utilities%20have%20motivation%20to%20inflate%20forecasts%2C%20he%20said%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bthe%20reasons%20for%20those%20biases%20have%20to%20do%20with%20real%20challenges%20to%20getting%20those%20forecasts%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20to%20remove%20some%20of%20the%20more%20speculative%20requests%2C%20according%20to%20experts%2C%20is%20to%20increase%20the%20financial%20disincentives%20for%20developers%20to%20submit%20multiple%20requests.%20In%20July%2C%20Ohio's%20public%20utilities%20commissions%20approved%20a%20settlement%20that%20requires%20data%20centers%20to%20pay%20for%20at%20least%2085%25%20of%20the%20electricity%20they%20say%20they%20need%2C%20even%20if%20they%20use%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20after%20the%20new%20rules%20went%20into%20effect%2C%20American%20Electric%20Power%20Ohio%20said%20it%20had%20gotten%20requests%20totalling%2013%20gigawatts%20of%20potential%20new%20load%2C%20less%20than%20half%20the%2030%20gigawatts%20of%20demand%20that%20it%20cited%20during%20the%20rule-making%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ohio%20settlement%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20of%20many%20new%20regulations%2C%20known%20as%20large%20load%20tariffs%2C%20now%20being%20considered%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20data%20center%20electricity%20demands.%20There%20are%20at%20least%2020%20under%20consideration%20across%20the%20US%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Sierra%20Club.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20some%20electricity%20customers%20are%20seeing%20costs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fenergy-conservation-hacks-data-center-costs-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskyrocket%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Customers%20who%20buy%20electricity%20from%20the%20regional%20electric%20grid%20managed%20by%20PJM%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20%247.3%20billion%20more%20for%20electricity%20thanks%20to%20data%20center%20concerns%2C%20according%20to%20a%20consulting%20firm%20that%20works%20with%20PJM.%20The%20total%20auction%20for%20future%20electricity%20supplies%20was%20a%20record%20%2416.1%20billion%20this%20year%2C%20up%20from%20the%20previous%20high%20of%20%2414.7%20billion%20set%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20basic%20conclusion%20of%20this%20analysis%20is%20that%20data%20center%20load%20growth%20is%20the%20primary%20reason%20for%20recent%20and%20expected%20capacity%20market%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%20wrote%20in%20its%20report%2C%20%26quot%3Bincluding%20total%20forecast%20load%20growth%2C%20the%20tight%20supply%20and%20demand%20balance%2C%20and%20high%20prices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sierra%20Club's%20Fisher%20said%20many%20stakeholders%20are%20beginning%20to%20wake%20up.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20starting%20to%20see%20is%20that%20both%20other%20ratepayer%20advocates%2C%20and%20commissions%2C%20and%20some%20utilities%2C%20are%20concerned%20about%20that%20potential%20for%20cross-subsidization%26quot%3B%20of%20data%20center%20costs%20to%20other%20customers%2C%20Fisher%20said.%20Rules%20like%20Ohio's%20are%20%26quot%3Ba%20mechanism%20of%20trying%20to%20block%20speculative%20customers%20or%20at%20least%20curtail%20speculative%20load%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20count%20that%20as%20a%20success.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-boom-bubble-power-utilities-forecasting-demand-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763460901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690cd26321c3f142ebfc375e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-boom-bubble-power-utilities-forecasting-demand-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Electricity%20forecasts%20have%20an%20inflation%20problem%20%E2%80%94%20and%20consumers%20could%20